  {# 5. Multi-nodes optimization campaigns #}
  <article>
    <header><h3>5. Multi-nodes optimization campaigns</h3></header>
    <p>
      Multiple data centers can concur to the same optimization study, requesting to the Hopaas client 
      a new set of hyperparameters to be tested and then communicating the outcome of the training.
      Several trials of one or more studies can be tracked and monitored by the hopaas instance. 
    </p>
